## 架构检查

### Domain 层无框架依赖

```bash
grep -r "org.springframework" src/domain/ || echo "✅ OK"
grep -r "jakarta.persistence" src/domain/ || echo "✅ OK"
grep -r "@Entity" src/domain/ || echo "✅ OK"
```

### 依赖方向正确

```
adapter/in → domain (依赖接口)
domain ← adapter/out (实现接口)
config → domain, adapter/in, adapter/out
```
